prompt_text: Describe the smartphone application that you use the most.
content_text: The smartphone application that I use the most is WhatsApp. I regularly use WhatsApp to interact my friends, my family and many other people in my life and. From the from that application, I used to convey my messages and some important information to the people to whom I have to interact and I also used to share jokes. I also used to share images to my friends, my colleagues, my WhatsApp group and I really like this app. It's very easy and convenient to use. I would suggest you also to use that app.
